              <p>Difficulty accessing quality help, unstructured practice, and opaque progress tracking.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card p-4 text-start">
              <h4 class="fw-semibold">For Tutors</h4>
              <p>Time-consuming prep work, poor student-tutor matches, and scheduling struggles.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Solutions -->
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h2 class="section-title title-solutions mb-4">Our AI-Enhanced Solutions</h2>
          <div class="d-grid gap-3">
            <div class="glass-card p-4 text-start">
              <h4 class="fw-semibold">Scalable Learning Support</h4>
              <p>AI-powered assistance ensures every student gets the help they need, when they need it.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-card p-4 text-start">
              <h4 class="fw-semibold">Intelligent Matching</h4>
              <p>Data-driven algorithms pair students with the perfect tutors based on learning style and needs.</p>
            </div>
